27:05.040 --> 27:07.475
“The instructions we have received 


27:07.475 --> 27:11.078
“at Jehovah’s hand over the past five months 


27:11.078 --> 27:14.881
“have far surpassed our expectations. 


27:14.882 --> 27:18.487
“Indeed, our hearts have been filled 


27:18.487 --> 27:21.355
“with so many good things!


27:21.355 --> 27:24.192
“When we started our training, 


27:24.192 --> 27:26.194
“Bible verses were 


27:26.193 --> 27:30.065
“like many isolated dots on a canvas. 


27:30.065 --> 27:32.067
“We have been taught 


27:32.067 --> 27:35.437
“how to connect them, 


27:35.437 --> 27:38.305
“revealing a marvelous picture. 


27:38.305 --> 27:40.608
“Moreover, we have learned 


27:40.608 --> 27:42.610
“how to work with Jehovah 


27:42.610 --> 27:44.612
“even more closely. 


27:44.612 --> 27:48.850
“We have also been taught how to display 


27:48.850 --> 27:51.585
“the mind of Christ more fully, 


27:51.585 --> 27:55.623
“especially by imitating his love 


27:55.623 --> 27:59.193
“when dealing with our brothers and sisters. 


27:59.193 --> 28:02.896
“Like Paul, we ask: 


28:02.897 --> 28:07.102
“‘What, then, 
are we to say about these things?’ 


28:07.102 --> 28:10.839
“We have mixed feelings: 


28:10.838 --> 28:12.973
“deep gratitude 


28:12.973 --> 28:17.145
“and a sense 
of insignificance overwhelm us, 


28:17.145 --> 28:19.447
“gratitude to you 


28:19.447 --> 28:21.750
“members of the Governing Body 


28:21.750 --> 28:24.685
“for your loving and honest counsel, 


28:24.685 --> 28:26.822
“gratitude to you 


28:26.822 --> 28:28.857
“our dear instructors 


28:28.857 --> 28:30.859
“for your tireless efforts 


28:30.858 --> 28:33.761
“to reach and touch our hearts, 


28:33.762 --> 28:36.264
“and gratitude to you 


28:36.263 --> 28:38.766
“dear members of the Bethel family. 


28:38.767 --> 28:43.672
“We will never forget your warm welcome 


28:43.672 --> 28:48.000
“and the way you included us in your family.


28:49.943 --> 28:52.880
“On the other hand, 
we feel insignificant 


28:52.880 --> 28:56.450
“in view of the greatness 
of Jehovah’s organization, 


28:56.450 --> 28:59.853
“insignificant as we begin to understand 


28:59.853 --> 29:02.290
