29:08.028 --> 29:10.465
“as we strive to apply 


29:10.465 --> 29:13.033
“all that we have learned. 


29:13.033 --> 29:15.436
“Furthermore, 


29:15.437 --> 29:18.339
“staying at Patterson for 20 weeks 


29:18.338 --> 29:20.841
“allowed us to feel the pulse 


29:20.842 --> 29:24.212
“of the earthly part 
of Jehovah’s organization. 


29:24.212 --> 29:27.649
“We have enjoyed the willing spirit 


29:27.648 --> 29:29.716
“of the many young ones 


29:29.717 --> 29:33.020
“and the wonderful example 
of faithful service 


29:33.020 --> 29:36.723
“of our older brothers and sisters. 


29:36.723 --> 29:39.260
“While working with you, 


29:39.260 --> 29:42.063
“we realized how much is accomplished 


29:42.063 --> 29:44.065
“behind the scenes. 


29:44.065 --> 29:46.167
“And we were deeply touched 


29:46.167 --> 29:49.104
