how the Governing Body 


29:49.103 --> 29:51.205
“genuinely cares 


29:51.205 --> 29:54.008
“for our dear brothers and sisters 


29:54.008 --> 29:56.076
“all over the world, 


29:56.077 --> 30:00.449
