30:51.065 --> 30:54.968
“our wish and pleasure 


30:54.968 --> 30:57.938
“to share these blessings 


30:57.938 --> 31:01.708
“with others in our assignments. 


31:01.708 --> 31:04.978
“Your brothers and sisters, 


31:04.978 --> 31:09.000
the 143rd class of Gilead.”


31:36.110 --> 31:38.478
It was definitely brought home to us today 


31:38.478 --> 31:41.916
that Jehovah is our Grand Instructor. 


31:41.917 --> 31:46.020
There is none like him 
in the entire universe. 


31:46.020 --> 31:49.957
He is so patient with us 
and so kind and so merciful 


31:49.957 --> 31:52.227
and definitely so loving. 


31:52.227 --> 31:55.797
He’s been good to us today, 


31:55.797 --> 32:00.669
and he’s going to be good for us forever. 


32:00.668 --> 32:02.870
So we’re just getting started. 


32:02.870 --> 32:05.440
We’re crawling. 


32:05.440 --> 32:07.842
But one of these days, we’ll get up 


32:07.842 --> 32:11.212
and we’ll walk and we’ll run. 


32:11.212 --> 32:13.982
Jehovah ranks the highest. 


32:13.982 --> 32:16.350
He was teaching not just you 


32:16.350 --> 32:18.720
but all of us today. 


32:18.720 --> 32:21.388
None of us as sinful humans 


32:21.388 --> 32:23.390
could say or speak the words 


32:23.390 --> 32:26.227
that touched our hearts without the help 


32:26.227 --> 32:28.462
of Jehovah’s holy spirit. 


32:28.462 --> 32:30.499
And there’s not a brother 


32:30.498 --> 32:34.935
that does not ask for that spirit, or sister, 


32:34.935 --> 32:38.000
who steps out here before God’s sheep 


32:39.907 --> 32:44.579
and gives any kind 
of encouragement or instruction.


32:44.578 --> 32:46.713
Jesus gave us the promise 


32:46.713 --> 32:50.083
at John 14:26, 


32:50.083 --> 32:53.788
and this is what he said. 


32:53.788 --> 32:56.000
Those of you who have your pads, 


32:57.992 --> 33:00.462
you’re already there. 


33:00.462 --> 33:03.597
I’m just getting there. 


33:03.597 --> 33:07.902
That’s John 14:26, which says: 


33:07.902 --> 33:09.870
“But the helper, the holy spirit, 


33:09.870 --> 33:12.273
“which the Father will send in my name, 


33:12.273 --> 33:15.141
“that one will teach you all things 


33:15.142 --> 33:17.712
“and bring back to your minds 


33:17.712 --> 33:20.000
all the things I told you.” 


33:21.282 --> 33:23.384
So 


33:23.383 --> 33:26.000
the holy spirit is going 
to help you remember. 


33:27.188 --> 33:30.000
Without it, you couldn’t remember. 


33:31.458 --> 33:34.595
But we pray for the holy spirit, 


33:34.595 --> 33:38.365
and it’s sent to us, and we remember. 


33:38.365 --> 33:40.768
Sometimes we’re shocked at how much 


33:40.768 --> 33:42.870
we can remember at a given time. 


33:42.870 --> 33:44.672
Well, it’s not us. 


33:44.672 --> 33:47.675
Somebody is helping us to remember, 


33:47.675 --> 33:50.412
and we must never forget that. 


33:50.412 --> 33:52.814
That promise 


33:52.813 --> 33:56.150
that Jesus gave way back then 


33:56.150 --> 33:59.453
held true not only for Jesus’ disciples 


33:59.453 --> 34:02.523
back then who loved him very much 


34:02.523 --> 34:05.125
but it holds true today 


34:05.125 --> 34:09.163
for those who love him as we do. 


34:09.163 --> 34:12.500
And we definitely love him. 


34:12.500 --> 34:14.602
There is just no doubt in our minds 


34:14.602 --> 34:17.239
about the love that we have in our hearts 


34:17.238 --> 34:21.008
for Jehovah God and Jesus. 


34:21.008 --> 34:24.000
It’s there.


34:25.245 --> 34:27.415
Jehovah opens our minds 


34:27.415 --> 34:29.583
and hearts to receive his Word. 


34:29.583 --> 34:33.286
Just think of the things that we’ve heard 


34:33.287 --> 34:35.824
from this platform today


34:35.823 --> 34:38.325
—things that touched the heart, 


34:38.325 --> 34:41.762
warmed the soul. 


34:41.762 --> 34:43.765
Jehovah was with us today 


34:43.765 --> 34:46.000
by means of his holy spirit. 


34:47.968 --> 34:50.070
Of course, this happened years ago 


34:50.070 --> 34:52.340
to a worshipper of Jehovah. 


34:52.340 --> 34:55.000
It wasn’t a male; it was a female. 


34:56.410 --> 35:01.000
At Acts 16:14, we find it’s Lydia. 


35:03.117 --> 35:05.987
It reads: “And a certain woman named Lydia, 


35:05.987 --> 35:08.957
“a seller of purple, of the city of Thyatira 


35:08.957 --> 35:12.994
“and a worshiper of God, was listening, 


35:12.993 --> 35:16.730
“and Jehovah opened her heart wide 


35:16.730 --> 35:19.500
“to pay attention to the things 


35:19.500 --> 35:21.902
being spoken by Paul.” 


35:21.902 --> 35:24.972
When Jehovah speaks 
and he opens our hearts, 


35:24.972 --> 35:27.242
we must not close our hearts 


35:27.242 --> 35:29.644
by failing to pay attention 


35:29.643 --> 35:34.681
to the brother that Jehovah 
is using to speak through. 


35:34.682 --> 35:36.184
If we’re not careful, 


35:36.183 --> 35:39.553
we just may close to that brother 


35:39.553 --> 35:43.390
because his tie is not straight, 


35:43.390 --> 35:47.000
his shoes are not shined. 


35:49.130 --> 35:51.132
That’s dangerous. 


35:51.132 --> 35:53.134
We want to listen to him. 


35:53.133 --> 35:55.703
Jehovah put him up there, 


35:55.703 --> 35:58.000
and we want to listen to what he has to say. 


35:59.273 --> 36:02.000
Don’t be so concerned with the way he looks. 


36:03.510 --> 36:06.047
If someone was concerned 
about the way a donkey looked, 


36:06.047 --> 36:08.749
he wouldn’t have paid any attention years ago 


36:08.748 --> 36:11.000
because Jehovah spoke through a donkey. 


36:12.620 --> 36:16.000
Donkeys are not the most beautiful animal. 


36:17.558 --> 36:19.593
But Jehovah chooses 


36:19.593 --> 36:22.095
what Jehovah wants to choose, 


36:22.095 --> 36:24.898
and he teaches lessons 


36:24.898 --> 36:27.066
for each and every one of us.


36:27.067 --> 36:29.504
Now, of course, when Lydia 


36:29.503 --> 36:32.773
was opening her heart 
by Jehovah’s help, 


36:32.773 --> 36:34.775
she’s looking at Paul. 


36:34.775 --> 36:38.845
But Paul may not have been 
the most handsome man to look at. 


36:38.845 --> 36:41.000
We don’t really know. 


36:42.082 --> 36:45.000
Some say that his eyebrows matched. 


36:46.987 --> 36:49.890
Others say he couldn’t see good. 


36:49.890 --> 36:52.927
Some say he was bald-headed. 


36:52.927 --> 36:55.162
We don’t really know. 


36:55.162 --> 37:00.000
One of these days we’ll know.


37:01.935 --> 37:04.738
Well, you’re no longer Gilead students 


37:04.738 --> 37:08.000
you are ex-Gilead students, 


37:10.177 --> 37:14.149
